events.title: Learn to Play: Tennis
events.description: Ever wanted to learn the basic skills of tennis or never had the chance pick up this amazing sport? You have the chance now UTM! This June and/or July join in on the 4-week UTM Beginner Tennis Lessons being offered by skilled tennis instructors on the UTM Tennis Courts. This is a great opportunity to learn the basics of tennis in a beginner friendly environment. Players will be introduced to the proper technique for volleys, serves, forehand and backhand groundstrokes.Don’t own a tennis racquet? Don’t worry… we have you covered! Please Note: This program is for novice/new players only.
